br />\n再耐啲之前有分金工木工<br />\n不過後來變DT，好多嘢冇教了<br />\n有兩部車床，未見開動過，而家已經移走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家啲中學仲有冇金工/木工堂上<br />\n以前中五讀工科會考要考埋D&amp;T<br />\n不過都係得幾百人考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家DSE都唔知有冇呢啲科考</blockquote><br />\n現時無分得咁專 某啲學校初中有科技堂 比啲所謂STEM習作你整之外 得高中有科選修叫設計與應用科技(老實講手工藝已經愈來愈少人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽聞呢科DSE每年大約得600-800名考生"},{"pid":"c007d88ca100d2b268d04ed0127518a1a2f024a8","tid":427460,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係間大型warehouse 超市 <br />\n乜撚DIY件 原料都有<br />\n已經贏香港十萬條街</blockquote><br />\n以前九龍灣都有間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nb&amp;q嘛，邊有得做丫<br />\n就算有時間都無地方擺架生去整<br />\n唔搵人上門搞 最多咪去宜家買現成野</blockquote><br />\n去宜家自己買傢私砌<br />\n已經係香港人嘅極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買宜家木家私可以自己改同上色都可以幾好玩"},{"pid":"d7517fe91629921cf5e632b7d6703d1a7df90df5","tid":427460,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學取撚消左木工堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最鍾意上DT</blockquote><br />\n再耐啲之前有分金工木工<br />\n不過後來變DT，好多嘢冇教了<br />\n有兩部車床，未見開動過，而家已經移走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家啲中學仲有冇金工/木工堂上<br />\n以前中五讀工科會考要考埋D&amp;T<br />\n不過都係得幾百人考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家DSE都唔知有冇呢啲科考</blockquote><br />\n現時無分得咁專 某啲學校初中有科技堂 比啲所謂STEM習作你整之外 得高中有科選修叫設計與應用科技(老實講手工藝已經愈來愈少人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽聞呢科DSE每年大約得600-800名考生</blockquote><br />\n金工木工呢啲係當年「實用中學」嘅產物<br />\n不過今時今日香港冇乜製造業，呢啲科變得不合時宜<br />\n其實有得揀，讀家政仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae0716122293aafa4126af6151b5703b117e18d","tid":427460,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"整鎗都識啦，glock 17基本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a96d72e2e2baa7c62f32815d70fbdc428f5cdc","tid":427460,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有冇個後花園俾你慢慢燒呀<br />\n上youtube見親啲人玩工藝嘢都係係啲較為空曠啲嘅地方搞<br />\n香港嘅話 試下係屋企入面搞木工 搞到一屋塵都似</blockquote><br />\n連噴模型油都無地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfe0322bb4f4cce09143ece2d75859875ff50a6","tid":427460,"uid":40250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港連讀engine果班都唔多整野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無空間練....<br />\n我最多都係買堆線同索掣自己砌control<br />\n木工要去工廈搵d班上"},{"pid":"661d2d7c41333b419a0e32a385765b5add0f9373","tid":427460,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"仲木工燒焊，3D print啦"},{"pid":"e91896588c2ce4e67adc1b6290734e8cf4122a1c","tid":427460,"uid":61051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港連讀engine果班都唔多整野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無空間練....<br />\n我最多都係買堆線同索掣自己砌control<br />\n木工要去工廈搵d班上</blockquote><br />\n廢青先有時間練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自製得多會有職業病 行街見到啲普通野 望多兩眼 估到大約原理 信自己整到就唔願比錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addb3d5a800c28a7425a52176089ee8e87e1dafe","tid":427460,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"香港都大把撚樣閪人個個都當自己識 IT programme 砌機"},{"pid":"45dc6a4f7842b334f975a2fc3ed74e3d9ec79421","tid":427460,"uid":6523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係間大型warehouse 超市 <br />\n乜撚DIY件 原料都有<br />\n已經贏香港十萬條街</blockquote><br />\n外國巴表示香港仲齊"},{"pid":"b35a290eb9624c5b94d184ffe51ec525183b99e9","tid":427460,"uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"因為唔識嗰啲冇拍片"},{"pid":"f704a3164543629e089206232703cd184641f8bf","tid":427460,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係間大型warehouse 超市 <br />\n乜撚DIY件 原料都有<br />\n已經贏香港十萬條街</blockquote><br />\n外國巴表示香港仲齊</blockquote><br />\n邊方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f2fe4c999eeccfdab889ee0b00debe32edb385","tid":427460,"uid":16760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"要買架生一樣行轉7記乜都買到 根本香港人就懶得整同買"},{"pid":"09c645d2a4540700e1c6e11415610c8034a6ff47","tid":427460,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"屌, 香港都大把人自已整啦"},{"pid":"f9e33452ebc416850ced260b9b8f5ad6fe041a3f","tid":427460,"uid":136355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國生活地廣人稀，<br />\n每個人獨立生存本能夠強。<br />\n通常天黑行出街已經冇乜人，<br />\n住偏遠些少更要自己處理大部份日常雜項!</blockquote><br />\n番工好慘"},{"pid":"e0d4934e8fd64859f2b176bdc306666642b59da9","tid":427460,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲木工燒焊，3D print啦</blockquote><br />\n我覺得學校應該教一啲基本工具嘅使用技巧、機械構造同埋各種材料嘅不同特性<br />\n呢啲都比較實用<br />\n3D打印除咗引起學生對科技嘅興趣之外，日常生活較少應用"},{"pid":"eab7647b0f567fb96810edafee8a39d16f81d2c3","tid":427460,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要買架生一樣行轉7記乜都買到 根本香港人就懶得整同買</blockquote><br />\n咩係7記"},{"pid":"11d01b00bdd052d636d6ac415fe48329c39c91e2","tid":427460,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"因為佢就係識先拍片<br />\n<br />\n同埋人地地方大<br />\n<br />\n有興趣玩既話係個車房整個workshop都得<br />\n<br />\n香港邊有得俾你咁玩<br />\n<br />\n想自學變相難左<br />\n<br />\n以前d人真係想玩又有錢會響工廠大廈租個單位工餘時間玩<br />\n<br />\n依加連工廈都貴租啦"},{"pid":"492f604a064e0c8f7cbdfdf4cb857216b4fc3e9d","tid":427460,"uid":15186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:43:03.000Z","msg":"上面好多都講哂 <br />\n另一個重點係搵人整好麻煩 星期六日人哋又唔一定開 局住自己整<br />\n加上老豆阿爺都自己整 由細睇到大 點都學到啲"},{"pid":"8f0357a8a42f278878e4ad99e61f7c8ee5384969","tid":427460,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲木工燒焊，3D print啦</blockquote><br />\n爆咗少少焊<br />\n你3D print有乜用?<br />\n成舊拎去換?"},{"pid":"b4625610316571798c2b2ea7b2e0da421390090e","tid":427460,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實，你係香港一個人住的話都一樣可以自學<br />\n淘寶買工具好平，係廁房鋸木，鋸完沖水就得，方便執手尾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搬去澄碧村.吉澳.荔枝窩既話<br />\n<br />\n可能就要迫住識少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26123652ec27c1b7ba84422980f300b4799a674f","tid":427460,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"香港地俾間大屋你住都無時間整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOT 完都累到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6cc4b4f8ae69de4d05512fb22dd6bd47486897","tid":427460,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬼佬夠以為我地個個都識功夫啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬼佬：當你日日都有警匪槍戰，你都會識功夫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼佬：石器時代咩仲功夫 直接燒槍啦！"},{"pid":"db8972e855e8245e5721fafa01a497fc6844e877","tid":427460,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"香港人搵時間試都無啦<br />\n日日ot 有時間不如留黎打機好過<br />\nDiy? 不了<br />\n用錢買時間算數<br />\n<br />\n利申：會自己唧下膠 工程人"},{"pid":"d9c67e23d640813b50d920386b823c8a2549cae7","tid":427460,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個花園擺到個20呎貨櫃裝雜物, 你都會識.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要份工唔洗ot，一個月有八日假喺屋企慢慢撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實一個月8日假唔夠撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲鬼佬一放假就好多日連假 好多AL<br />\n唔似香港人 得果10日 12日"},{"pid":"a83ebe3a69d1ff3621a025968b1d6e569342345c","tid":427460,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港連讀engine果班都唔多整野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry囉"},{"pid":"b0137c20c40740f270a243c36796b84c7005376d","tid":427460,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你個花園擺到個20呎貨櫃裝雜物, 你都會識.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要份工唔洗ot，一個月有八日假喺屋企慢慢撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實一個月8日假唔夠撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲鬼佬一放假就好多日連假 好多AL<br />\n唔似香港人 得果10日 12日</blockquote><br />\n做野慢 多精力 少ot 6點準時收工  又多唔同節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43024a22c87caefbd74e6c076e2cb9869ee971c7","tid":427460,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實外國主要係有地方試同易搵工具玩 正常你夠膽試都會識 但可惜香港好多人無試既機會<br />\n<br />\n之前去美國見有間叫The Home Depot  木又買到 工具又買到 方便過香港百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:半個maker</blockquote><br />\n第一次去Home depot逐個貨架睇。可以睇半日"},{"pid":"e17287bb525ffbeec736b177c8110a9cc490f7d7","tid":427460,"uid":61051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實外國主要係有地方試同易搵工具玩 正常你夠膽試都會識 但可惜香港好多人無試既機會<br />\n<br />\n之前去美國見有間叫The Home Depot  木又買到 工具又買到 方便過香港百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:半個maker</blockquote><br />\n第一次去Home depot逐個貨架睇。可以睇半日</blockquote><br />\n係呀 每次過去都總有大半日專行Home depot<br />\n我地稱果度為 男人既天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a00db29a3ad4a0764f82b064b06e564dfd9b33","tid":427460,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:31:21.000Z","msg":"以前中學都有學 咩虎鉗, 亞加力膠... 後尾轉哂學Auto cat姐...<br />\n依家中學應該教人點用3D printer 去整野喇"}]}